Package: gsDesignNB
Title: Sample Size Calculation and Simulation for Negative Binomial Outcomes
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Keaven", "Anderson", email = "keaven_anderson@merck.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Keaven Anderson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Keaven Anderson <keaven_anderson@merck.com>
Description: Provides sample size calculation methods for negative binomial outcomes,
    including the methods by Zhu and Lakkis (2014) and Friede and Schmidli (2010).
    Supports piecewise constant accrual rates.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://keaven.github.io/gsDesignNB/
